### 解析单个证书信息（含到期剩余天数）

POST http://localhost:8080/parse-cert
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "certPath": "e:\\temp\\record13\\426\\test.cer"
}

### 校验证书链完整性（服务端证书 + 中间证书 + root 证书）

POST http://localhost:8080/verify-cert-chain
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "certPath": "e:\\temp\\record13\\426\\server.pem",
    "intermediateCertPaths": [
        "e:\\temp\\record13\\426\\intermediate.pem"
    ],
    "rootCertPaths": [
        "e:\\temp\\record13\\426\\root.pem"
    ]
}

### 仅校验自签名根证书（不提供中间和 root 证书）

POST http://localhost:8080/verify-cert-chain
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "certPath": "e:\\temp\\record13\\426\\test.cer"
}
